name: MONEY MASK. CUSTOM SOLID SILVER PENDANT AND 24"CHAIN
description:
Product Description
These necklaces feature the same handmade from beginning to end approach that all of our solid sterling silver jewelry does. The chain and pendant are all .925 italian silver and are handcrafted to last a lifetime .The chain is a seamless style snake type that is thick but not too chunky . it falls gracefully off the neck line and showcases the money mask design that has become so popular it has jumped from off tee shirts to custom jewelry . pictures dont speak enough words to show all the attention to detail that goes into just one piece. each unique in its own way each one hand crafted on eat a time. no casting here!

name: CUTHROAT CREST TEE
description:
Product Description
The cuthroat crest is the international symbol for cuthroat's everywhere. it features the W D G A S on the front underneath a very large screenprint on front . on back the shirt says Cuthroat Clothing in godfather style writing and beneath that it says "We dont give a shit" to further explain the front. this is a high quality screenprinted gildan tee. featuring a two color print on the front and back
